                        </li>
                        <li>REGULATORY COMPLIANCE AND VERIFICATION
                            <ul>
                                <li>In response to the scale and effect of money laundering the Hong Kong Government, in common with many other countries, has passed legislation designed to prevent money laundering and to combat terrorism. Although Tradecoin4u is currently unregulated and does not fall within the scope of the AML/KYC obligations in Hong Kong, we have put in place systems and procedures that meet the Hong Kong AML legislation.</li>
